---
description: Express + SQLite API conventions for this project
alwaysApply: true
---

- Express server; SQLite via `better-sqlite3` + Drizzle ORM (schema in `src/schema.ts`, queries in `src/db.ts`)
- Seed test data in tests, not in production startup
- Every new endpoint ships with an npm test that hits it
- Run `npm test` as the done-when check before accepting a diff